name: Fighter Being
description:
Where there is magic, treasures, secrets, there should be battles too. To win a battle you need a party and that party needs a Fighter to stay in front. This First Light Fighter Being would not only frontline on the battlefront but also give advantage in this tavern called HEN.

As a <light> being it is respected by all and This <light> <fighter> being lets you hire/collect other <fighter> beings by an offer with 1 tez discount.



Character from a live performance from Fireter - a theater of shadow and fire. 

Also a <light> <fighter> <first>
